USAGE="Usage: ${bold}pkg blacklist PKGNAME${endcolour}

Add PKGNAME to the blacklist.

The blacklist is a list of packages that Pkg 
will always ignore.

The blacklist can be found at:

${bold}\$HOME/.pkg/blacklisted_packages${endcolour}

You can remove a package from the blacklist using:

  ${bold}pkg whitelist PKGNAME${endcolour}


Here is your current blacklist:

${yellow}$(\cat ~/.pkg/blacklisted_packages)${endcolour}"
